      <p>Non-profits have recognized the value of technical and design talent in the efficiency and scalability of services in the public sector. These organizations have taken on an advocacy, advisory, training and/or talent scout role for the government. The list of non-profits below, source and place talent in all levels of the public sector with skills ranging from data science to software development to human centered design and public policy. The orgnaizations post fellowship or internship opportunities once or twice a year, so please follow them closely.</p>


